      <title>摩根大通的米斯拉认为风险资产将关注利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-03/jpm-s-misra-sees-risk-assets-paying-attention-to-rates-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通核心债券 ETF 投资组合经理 Priya Misra 解释了她认为导致美国 10 年期债券收益率接近 5% 的因素对风险资产来说是一个问题的原因。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-03/jpm-s-misra-sees-risk-assets-paying-attention-to-rates-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 12:38:58 GMT</pubDate>
